No. 09-804. CIGNA Corporation, et al., Petitioners v. Janice C. Amara, et al., Individually and on Behalf of All Others Similarly Situated. 561 U.S. 1024, 130 S. Ct. 3500,

177 L. Ed. 2d 1113,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 5324. June 28, 2010.

Petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit granted.

Same case below, 348 Fed. Appx. 627.
